metadata.name: Fascinating Kim
metadata.description:
She´s Kim.From Canada and she´s 25 Years
When I designed Kim with this dress, I needed to design a suitable black dress with silk ,feathers for her, and for the back of the page, I painted purple, which is my favorite, and blue, which is the favorite color of the girl's character.  Wind on the left and her hair is blowing falling out. The girl has fallen in love with colored bubbles and wants to grab them with her hand.
Don't be impressed by money, followers, degrees and titles. Be impressed by humility integrity, generosity and kindness.
The final loopable output is generated from my original adobe 
2500x3000 px
